{"tid":1536224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"極重要戰線 手足請入","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:22:44.000Z","uid":26413,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6d472fe4b366775b2d5bf0b51815b72c771de16","tid":1536224,"uid":26413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"發夢見到我個公務員朋友, 佢話搞不合作運動, 應該拜訪: <br />\n<br />\n政府化驗所.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtlab.gov.hk/chinese/home.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtlab.gov.hk%2Fchinese%2Fhome.htm&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=5162c2ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtlab.gov.hk/chinese/home.htm</a> <br />\n<br />\n佢地負責: <br />\nDNA親子鑑定 -  每日150個大陸人嚟香港都係靠佢地<br />\n<br />\n保管賊贓及毒品 - 用作上庭之用<br />\n<br />\n地址在何文田, 冇黑警守衛<br />\n<br />\n我諗除左税局, 另一好去處.<br />\n<br />\n要post到人知，因為太子條cctv好有機會都係喺何文田"},{"pid":"19b0f5c84dd474c11f0436860fa13fcefe01fe30","tid":1536224,"uid":26413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"339317ac3db8f637f47d4bf680d5c05e4ccca6ea","tid":1536224,"uid":26413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ba564b47912ec56a0e998514b0e3a0f23eacb0","tid":1536224,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gi